#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:2
#: f9299d395b664ce7be442be66333ddec
msgid "Geomechanics: Drucker-Prager triaxial compression"
msgstr "岩土力学：Drucker-Prager 三轴压缩"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:4
#: 7391c6cb6c824abfb4bb1c0117f29d74
msgid ""
"This example introduces a small geomechanics application inside the solid-"
"mechanics example family.  It uses TensorMesh's public Drucker-Prager API — "
"the :class:`~tensormesh.assemble.DruckerPragerPlasticity` assembler, the "
":class:`~tensormesh.material.FrictionalMaterial` container, and the "
"constitutive primitive "
":func:`~tensormesh.functional.plastic.drucker_prager_yield_value` — to drive"
" a pressure-dependent soil or weak-rock material through a simple triaxial-"
"compression strain path."
msgstr ""
"本示例在固体力学示例族中引入一个小型岩土力学应用。它使用 TensorMesh 的公共 Drucker-Prager API —— "
":class:`~tensormesh.assemble.DruckerPragerPlasticity` 装配器、\\ "
":class:`~tensormesh.material.FrictionalMaterial` 容器,以及本构原语 "
":func:`~tensormesh.functional.plastic.drucker_prager_yield_value` —— "
"驱动压力相关的土体或软岩材料经历一条简单的三轴压缩应变路径。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:12
#: 9ea68c48c2274b00a6047850efde1c10
msgid ""
"The goal is deliberately modest: demonstrate TensorMesh conventions for "
"geomechanics on a minimal driver.  The example script lives in "
"``examples/solid/geomechanics/drucker_prager_triaxial/drucker_prager_triaxial.py``."
msgstr ""
"目标刻意保持适度:在一个极简驱动上演示 TensorMesh 的岩土力学约定。示例脚本位于 "
"``examples/solid/geomechanics/drucker_prager_triaxial/drucker_prager_triaxial.py``\\"
" 。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:17
#: e98f084760e941b7b3f447820d37e783
msgid "Problem"
msgstr "问题"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:19
#: d1151108e9234e578c58fafc39d7759a
msgid ""
"The model is small-strain, associated Drucker-Prager plasticity with linear "
"isotropic hardening.  TensorMesh keeps the internal solid-mechanics "
"convention stress tension-positive.  For geomechanics reporting, the script "
"prints axial stress and mean pressure as compression-positive quantities."
msgstr ""
"模型为小应变、关联 Drucker-Prager 塑性，并带有线性各向同性硬化。TensorMesh "
"内部保持固体力学约定：应力以受拉为正。为便于岩土力学报告，脚本将轴向应力和平均压力以受压为正的形式输出。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:24
#: 880edccf9dee4d95bdad74f8f21fd431
msgid "The yield function is written internally as"
msgstr "屈服函数在内部写为"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:26
#: 7bb9d5bca3284c029b9ae72376ac61b1
msgid "f(\\sigma, \\alpha) = q + \\eta I_1 - (k + H\\alpha) \\le 0,"
msgstr "f(\\sigma, \\alpha) = q + \\eta I_1 - (k + H\\alpha) \\le 0,"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:30
#: 21eadc3dc1ba48b0b9f40f4db36d4012
msgid "where"
msgstr "其中"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:32
#: 807e96d7ad8a47248c4608b4ff3c3140
msgid ""
"I_1 = \\mathrm{tr}(\\sigma), \\qquad\n"
"q = \\sqrt{\\frac{3}{2}\\,s:s}, \\qquad\n"
"p = -\\frac{I_1}{3}."
msgstr ""
"I_1 = \\mathrm{tr}(\\sigma), \\qquad\n"
"q = \\sqrt{\\frac{3}{2}\\,s:s}, \\qquad\n"
"p = -\\frac{I_1}{3}."

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:38
#: 03dd1c226e8f487ab0f9376e3667cf3c
msgid ""
"Because compression gives negative ``I1`` in the tension-positive "
"convention, higher confinement lowers ``f`` and delays yielding."
msgstr "由于在受拉为正约定下受压会导致 ``I1`` 为负，更高的围压会降低 ``f`` 并延迟屈服。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:42
#: ff1eb9b6dd2a4c038fd1e547a552bb3f
msgid "History variables"
msgstr "历史变量"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:44
#: 9e98d9dfde9e44be97c96b763569ed98
msgid ""
"The built-in assembler follows the same lifecycle as the J2 plasticity "
"model:"
msgstr "该内置装配器遵循与 J2 塑性模型相同的生命周期:"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:46
#: 84cf6eb5a20949f5804aa991b465ef2c
msgid ""
"per-quadrature history variables are stored in ``model.history[etype]``;"
msgstr "逐求积点历史变量存储在 ``model.history[etype]`` 中;"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:47
#: e9969a1ad4f6480ea27848e732825142
msgid ""
"previous-step ``eps_p`` and ``alpha`` are passed through ``element_data`` "
"(via ``model.element_data_from_history()``);"
msgstr ""
"上一步的 ``eps_p`` 和 ``alpha`` 通过 ``element_data`` 传入(经由 "
"``model.element_data_from_history()``);"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:49
#: 7aa3214f128b4e699529f91195289895
msgid ""
"``update_state(u)`` is called after each converged load step under "
"``torch.no_grad()``."
msgstr "``update_state(u)`` 在每个收敛的载荷步结束后，于 ``torch.no_grad()`` 上下文中被调用。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:53
#: bbbde41046494e61a0acb94966bcd715
msgid "Sanity check"
msgstr "合理性检验"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:55
#: 4d64c215fba04414acdd73b91b91bfe1
msgid "Two confinement levels are run:"
msgstr "运行两种围压水平："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:57
#: 1bb6792689064fc286591860fd76bb84
msgid "``p0 = 0 kPa``;"
msgstr "``p0 = 0 kPa``\\ ；"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:58
#: a2db93ab73be4269893059981c9d8103
msgid "``p0 = 100 kPa``."
msgstr "``p0 = 100 kPa``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:60
#: 532919342edd471ba17e5225bcd64c2e
msgid ""
"The script checks that the higher-confinement case reaches the elastic trial"
" yield surface later and that the committed plastic history variable is "
"monotonic."
msgstr "脚本验证更高围压的情况更晚到达弹性试探屈服面，且提交的塑性历史变量是单调的。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:64
#: 8ddb22eb5fbe4071bbfdf6b1038b80ef
msgid "Running it"
msgstr "运行"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:71
#: 6b946f0a874343f9bfe0891c496ceea0
msgid "For a fast numerical-only run without writing the plot:"
msgstr "若仅进行快速数值计算而不输出图像："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:77
#: e49a1a83c45d4c0c9da54b50ec8418d0
msgid ""
"The default run writes ``drucker_prager_triaxial.png`` with axial stress and"
" plastic-history curves."
msgstr "默认运行会写入 ``drucker_prager_triaxial.png``\\ ，其中包含轴向应力与塑性历史曲线。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:80
#: 8a2c658fd6194329849a07243f78345b
msgid ""
"Drucker-Prager triaxial compression response showing axial stress and "
"plastic history for two confinement levels"
msgstr "Drucker-Prager 三轴压缩响应,显示两种围压水平下的轴向应力与塑性历史"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:84
#: f0a271640db94087a338db8d61081fbf
msgid ""
"Output of ``drucker_prager_triaxial.py``. The left panel shows the "
"compression-positive axial stress response; the right panel shows the "
"committed plastic history variable. The higher-confinement case yields "
"later, matching the pressure-dependent Drucker-Prager sanity check."
msgstr ""
"``drucker_prager_triaxial.py`` "
"的输出。左面板显示压缩为正的轴向应力响应;右面板显示提交的塑性历史变量。围压更高的情形屈服更晚,符合压力相关的 Drucker-Prager "
"合理性检验。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:90
#: 716c341deb8f42348636e1d373bb7b5b
msgid "Core implementation"
msgstr "核心实现"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:92
#: 1295389b9c5f4ee7b1037108e6cc00d7
msgid ""
"The driver builds a :class:`~tensormesh.material.FrictionalMaterial`, "
"assembles the built-in :class:`~tensormesh.assemble.DruckerPragerPlasticity`"
" model, and steps the strain path while committing history with "
"``update_state``:"
msgstr ""
"该驱动构建一个 :class:`~tensormesh.material.FrictionalMaterial`,装配内置的 "
":class:`~tensormesh.assemble.DruckerPragerPlasticity` 模型,并在用 "
"``update_state`` 提交历史的同时步进应变路径:"

